Package
Description
Battleship
This system simulates playing a game of Battleship between two players.
Battleship.Controller
This package contains all classes relating to controlling a Battleship game.
Battleship.game
This package contains all classes that model a game of Battleship.
Battleship.game.GameBoard
This package represents all classes relating to all game boards.
Battleship.game.Ships
This package contains all Ship classes.
Battleship.GameIO
This package contains all classes to handle all IO for the game
Battleship.GameIO.Validators
This package handles all input validation from the user.
Battleship.GameIO.Views
This package handles all views generated for the game.
